Subject: [PATCH 2/2] petsc4py: fix leaks in test

---
 src/binding/petsc4py/test/test_mat_py.py | 75 +++++++++++++-----------
 1 file changed, 40 insertions(+), 35 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/binding/petsc4py/test/test_mat_py.py b/src/binding/petsc4py/test/test_mat_py.py
